{\b\fs28 Technical Requirements: AI-Powered Invoice Processing Automation\par}
\par
{\b\fs26 Project Overview\par}
Automate the manual invoice processing workflow using AI to extract data, validate information, and route approvals for our accounts payable department.\par
\par
{\b\fs26 Current Architecture & Systems\par}
\par
{\b Existing System Architecture\par}
{\b Architecture Pattern:} Microservices architecture deployed on AWS\par
{\b Core Platforms:}\par
\tab ERP System: SAP S/4HANA (on-premise)\par
\tab Document Management: SharePoint Online\par
\tab Email System: Microsoft Exchange Online\par
\tab Database: PostgreSQL 12 on AWS RDS\par
{\b Cloud Maturity:} Hybrid cloud setup with 60% workloads on AWS, 40% on-premise\par
{\b Current Integration Patterns:}\par
\tab REST APIs for external integrations\par
\tab Message queues using Amazon SQS for asynchronous processing\par
\tab File-based integration for legacy systems\par
\par
