{\b API Gateway:} AWS API Gateway for external APIs\par
{\b Internal APIs:} 15+ microservices with REST endpoints\par
{\b Authentication:} OAuth 2.0 with JWT tokens\par
{\b Rate Limiting:} 1000 requests/minute per client\par
\par
